    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "6c933991-2c2b-4b83-8949-9929c7d75d79",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "46e33cd4-cb0c-4538-b793-2e7e25d73dc5",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "585e69b4-026c-44bd-98ee-e03bcb133ad1",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For today's lesson, you will learn how to construct a Sol runestone. This spell creates a flash of light that does significant damage each round, affecting creatures such as Undead that are affected by sunlight.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f5889136-bc6f-48dc-a6e4-65e5c6c9f32e",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Like the Frigida runestone, you place it upon the ground and say the runestone's name. Whenever an Undead creature comes within the aura of the runestone, the spell will be set off.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "09bd8dde-728e-4c57-95bb-efbf464ba9b4",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Do you have any questions or comments before we proceed with the construction of the Sol runestone?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "667b1394-a66a-4114-8e19-5acf6f27a0dc",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "14a68614-b045-4084-9adc-c3cb55e81429",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "2edf3b56-46b4-4ffd-b862-38ab1499c9d8",
                            "text": "Ask About the Spell Damage",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "371b6f1e-ab35-41bb-8357-ca5e27994307",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Does this Sol runestone do any damage to living creatures?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5116961d-4292-4250-b214-3a4bcd5a07e0",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The spell creates a field of concentrated sunlight. Living creatures might only get a bit sunburned by the spell, but they are momentarily blinded. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "87cb9e86-d423-41d0-aab7-7104957f71f8",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, since Undead cannot abide sunlight, they are seriously wounded by the light.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "67980b17-a76b-4e56-ad03-aa5ed134868b",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "2ea1ab02-f597-4e1e-8885-12976d5f1744",
                            "text": "Ask About the Spell Effect",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "dfc88524-45c3-4f96-a251-a4d0e79f00c1",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Wouldn't the bright light of the spell blind everything around the runestone?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "987257b8-9d9f-4c49-b62f-99052fab1a36",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It seems reasonable to think that a bright light in a dark room would blind about everyone that looks upon it. Oddly enough, the light only shines brightly when you are within the spell effect area.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "adb8a393-5f06-407c-a36a-eba934f242d1",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It has to do with the mathematics of magic. If you are interested, I could go into the math that explains the phenomenon...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "bacee7fb-f1b1-4d8c-9a58-7db61de880ad",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "I think I've had enough explanation for now, thank you.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "6569a157-164e-4078-82b5-2531466f6bfc",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "10b7d987-bc41-453e-8c99-3196797219bd",
                            "text": "Make a Joke About Wizards",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6caf9177-74ef-4f03-b297-279d1713643d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "What did the Wizard say after her crystal ball remained cloudy as she tried to get her client to come to an agreement?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1392bf11-99da-4298-81ff-44c1fc9eb8d9",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I assume this is not a serious question.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d8c2ad22-4a1e-4fca-9d9d-ffa2ca2848ae",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "The Wizard said, \"If at first you don't concede, scry, scry again!\"",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
