                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "94c0f853-9c55-4478-8e0b-0f62301c5f4c",
                    "name": "Sol Support",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "We learned how to make a Sol Rune. It is placed on the ground and if some Undead ugly buggly moves over it, it flashes a light and hurts the monster. If it's a living monster, it just blinds them for a short while. This could be useful, but not as useful as it could be if it just exploded and blew the monster to gooey bits. "
                },
                {
